<bibRefCitation author="Speight" box="[1113,1271,1198,1223]" pageId="47" pageNumber="198" refString="Speight, M. C. D. (2013) Species accounts of European Syrphidae (Diptera), 2013. Syrph the Net, the database of European Syrphidae, vol. 72, Syrph the Net publications, Dublin, 316 pp." type="book" year="2013">Speight 2013</bibRefCitation>
